float PyStreamPSA::halfLife ( void   )  const

This is the python Get-Accessor for the half-life property of the StreamPSA.

This property is the time in seconds for the current velocity of the particle to reach half-way towards the streamPSA's velocity.

Returns:
A value in seconds.
